data.description: Charming 2 Bedroom Ranch-Style Townhome with Attached 2-Car Garage in Kokomo, IN  Welcome to your new home! This lovely 2-bedroom ranch-style townhome offers the perfect blend of comfort and convenience. With a host of desirable features, including a delightful porch, an attached 2-car garage, open floor plan, and a prime location near shopping, this property is a true gem.  Key Features:1. Inviting Porch: Start your day with a cup of coffee on the charming porch, a perfect spot to enjoy the morning sun or unwind in the evening.  2. Spacious 2-Car Garage: No more worries about parking or storage space. The attached 2-car garage provides convenience and security for your vehicles and belongings.  3. Open Floor Plan: The open and airy floor plan creates a warm and welcoming ambiance. The seamless flow between the living, dining, and kitchen areas allows for easy entertaining and a sense of togetherness.  4. Vaulted Ceilings: The vaulted ceilings add a touch of elegance to the living space, creating an open and spacious feel throughout the home.  5. No stairs, great lay-out  6. Double Sink in Master Bathroom: The master bedroom boasts a stylish en-suite bathroom with a convenient double sink, making your morning routine a breeze.  7. Prime Location: townhome is just moments away from shopping centers, restaurants, and recreational opportunities. You'll have everything you need right at your doorstep.  Don't miss the opportunity to make this fantastic 2-bedroom townhome your own. It's the perfect place to enjoy the benefits of single-level living with modern amenities, all in a well-maintained and desirable location.
